CustomField.description: Specifies the Template Unique Name of the email template to use for team schedule notifications. If no template is defined, a system-generated email template for notifications is used that includes the team schedule time slot names, start times, and end times. Note that you can override the template at a team level with the Custom Template Name (Schedule) field on the Team object.
CustomField.inlineHelpText: Specifies the Template Unique Name of the email template to use for team schedule notifications.
CustomField.label: Email Template (Schedule)
